     C                   IF        PK0OPCI<>' 1' AND PK0OPCI<>'1 '                                  
     C                   IF        PK0ARTI<>*BLANKS                                                 
     C                             OR PK0VARI<>*BLANKS  OR PK0MODE<>*BLANKS                         
