     C                   ELSE                                                                       
     C                   EVAL      S032FRRE=*BLANKS                                                 
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
     C                   EVAL      S032TPLA=S5TPLA                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S032ARTI=S5ARTI                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S032VARI=S5VARI                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S032MODE=S5MODE                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S032TCOJ=S5TCOJ                                                  
