     C                   ENDSL                                                                      
      *                                                                                             
     C                   EVAL      S062DES1=S5DES1                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S062ARTI=S5ARTI                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S062VARI=S5VARI                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S062MODE=S5MODE                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S062TCOJ=S5TCOJ                                                  
     C                   EVAL      S062TPPR=S5TPPR                                                  
C1663C                   EVAL      S062TPRM=S5TPRM                                                  
                                                                                                    
