31712C                   PARM      *ZEROS        @PEFDDS                                            
31712C                   PARM                    @PECANT                                            
31712C                   PARM      S5UNIM        @PEUNIM                                            
31712C                   PARM      S5LOGE        @PELOGE                                            
31712C                   PARM      *BLANKS       @PETPLA                                            
C2170C*31712             PARM      '*'           @PERRO                                             
